menuconfig SYSTEMCMDS_WK2132_TEST
	bool "wk2132_test"
	default n
	---help---
		Enable support for WK2132 UART test utility

		This command provides comprehensive testing capabilities for the WK2132
		I2C-to-UART bridge used in wheel loader serial communication systems.

		Test modes include:
		- Basic connectivity test
		- Loopback test (requires hardware loopback)
		- Echo test (requires external echo device)
		- Pattern transmission test
		- Continuous transmission test
